# ARTI 308 - Lab 2

## Machine Learning Problem
This project aims to predict whether a passenger survived the Titanic disaster based on passenger information such as age, gender, class, and fare.

This is a classification problem because the target variable (Survived) has two categories: 0 (did not survive) and 1 (survived).

## Dataset
Titanic Dataset from GitHub (Data Science Dojo).

## Files Included
- Google Colab Notebook
- Methodology Diagram
